Brook Learning Trust and its academies are committed to advancing and achieving equality of opportunity 
for all we serve. We believe that all people are of equal value and are entitled to equality of opportunity 
and that our diversity enriches our community. Brook Learning Trust is committed to equal pay, and a fair 
and open recruitment process which is free from discrimination.   

I confirm that the above information has been prepared from our payroll data from the snapshot date of 
24 March 2017 and fairly represents the gender pay gap information for Brook Learning Trust. 

 

 
 
